Class Coverage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseElement
      • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseResource
        • ca.uhn.fhir.model.dev.resource.Coverage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class Coverage
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR Coverage Resource (Insurance or medical plan)

    Definition: Financial instrument which may be used to pay for or reimburse for health care products and services.

    Requirements: Health care programs and insurers are significant payors of health service costs

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/Coverage
